    <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Created by <strong style="color:#fff;">Nexora</strong></p>
    <span class="discord-badge"><i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i> @@ftw.sadistic</span>

    <p class="description" style="max-width: 800px; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        This tool is built using <strong>UnityPy</strong> &amp; <strong>Pyodide</strong> and provides asset viewing capabilities
        similar to Asset Studio, directly within your browser.
    </p>

    <p class="warning">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
        Asset editing functionality is currently in experimental stages and may not function as intended.
        Improvements are planned for future updates.
    </p>

</div>
